This cookie is used to store configuration settings for VWO tests running on the site. It helps in managing the version of the site or page that a user should receive as part of the testing process, ensuring that the user sees the correct variant consistently. This cookie also helps in tracking the performance of different web page variations and can store data such as the percentage of traffic to assign to each variant, the goal of the test, and other related parameters.
_vwo_ds
Collects data on the user's visits to the website, such as the number of visits, average time spent on the website and what pages have been loaded with the purpose of generating reports for optimising the website content.
