Welcome
Come here for information throughout the shopping experience to learn more about what to expect when bringing goods into Ireland.
Duties and Taxes
In Ireland you can spend up to 150 EUR and not incur any duty on your order. VAT is 23% and due on any order above 0 EUR.
As you add items to your cart, you can return here to get more detailed calculations on possible duty and VAT.
